t-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img fetchpriority=\"high\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"290\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/disc-check-valves.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2834\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/disc-check-valves.jpg 500w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/disc-check-valves-300x174.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f3b302 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5f3b302\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e90c5ef animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e90c5ef\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engineered for Performance<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-986fa25 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"986fa25\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Disc Check Valves FMDCV<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d8e3815 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d8e3815\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>A flanged metal disc check valve is a type of check valve used to prevent backflow in pipelines. When fluid flows in the desired direction, the disc inside the valve lifts, allowing the fluid to pass through. When flow stops or reverses, the disc closes under its own weight or with the assistance of a spring, preventing backflow.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0b22338 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"0b22338\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1bd9d2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"f1bd9d2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-80cbbef e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"80cbbef\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5669569 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"5669569\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3f155f2 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3f155f2\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ef2e4d0 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"ef2e4d0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Feature<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-247cf5e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"247cf5e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>\u2022 FMDCVs typically come with flanged ends, allowing for easy installation and connection to piping systems using bolts and nuts.<\/p><p>\u2022 FMDCVs are constructed with durable metal materials such as carbon steel, stainless steel, ductile iron, or bronze, ensuring robustness and resistance to corrosion and erosion.<\/p><p>\u2022 FMDCVs feature a swing disc design that allows for smooth operation and low pressure drop. The disc swings freely on a hinge or pivot to allow forward flow while preventing backflow.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d37ed0 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"4d37ed0\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-169c3af animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"169c3af\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Benefits<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f0d4135 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f0d4135\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>\u2022 FMDCVs provide reliable backflow prevention by allowing fluid to flow in one direction while automatically closing to prevent reverse flow. This helps maintain system integrity and prevents contamination of fluids.<\/p><p>\u2022 The design of FMDCVs typically results in low pressure drop across the valve, minimizing energy losses and optimizing system efficiency.<\/p><p>\u2022 FMDCVs can be installed in a wide range of applications and industries, including water distribution, wastewater treatment, HVAC systems, industrial processes, and more. They are suitable for various fluid types and operating conditions.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-41a8e29 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"41a8e29\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;background_background&quot;:&quot;classic&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3b6cdf6 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"3b6cdf6\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b4a1939 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"b4a1939\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6fccbca elementor-widget elementor-widget-image\" data-id=\"6fccbca\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"image.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img decoding=\"async\" width=\"500\" height=\"290\" src=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/forbes-marshall-safety-relief-valve-fmsrv.jpg\" class=\"attachment-large size-large wp-image-2835\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/forbes-marshall-safety-relief-valve-fmsrv.jpg 500w, https:\/\/Navjivanvalves.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2025\/04\/forbes-marshall-safety-relief-valve-fmsrv-300x174.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 500px) 100vw, 500px\" \/>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ac0ef5a e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"ac0ef5a\" data-element_type=\"container\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f16376c animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f16376c\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Engineered for Performance<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f054db5 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"f054db5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Forbes Marshall Safety Relief Valve FMSRV<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8fe21b1 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"8fe21b1\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>The primary function of the FMSRV is to protect equipment and systems from overpressure situations by relieving excess pressure. The valve operates automatically in response to predetermined pressure levels. When the pressure inside the system exceeds the setpoint, the valve opens to discharge the excess pressure.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e7fc877 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"e7fc877\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">1. FMSRV (DN 15) Forbes Marshall Safety Relief Valve<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-aa94482 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"aa94482\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>The Forbes Marshall Safety Relief Valve (FMSRV) with a DN 15 designation refers to a specific model of safety relief valve manufactured by Forbes Marshall, with a nominal diameter (DN) of 15. The DN 15 designation indicates the nominal diameter of the valve, which is 15 millimeters. This size is suitable for applications where smaller flow rates or pipe sizes are involved.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-57b207e animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"57b207e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">2. FMSRV (DN20-50) Forbes Marshall Safety Relief Valve<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-daecb10 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"daecb10\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>The Forbes Marshall Safety Relief Valve (FMSRV) with a DN20-50 designation refers to a series of safety relief valves manufactured by Forbes Marshall, covering a range of nominal diameters from DN20 to DN50.The DN20-50 designation indicates that the FMSRV series covers a range of nominal diameters from DN20 to DN50. This range allows for flexibility in selecting the appropriate valve size based on the specific application requirements, flow rates, and pipe sizes.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3723024 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"3723024\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Features<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5f13fe5 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5f13fe5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>\u2022 The primary function of the FMSRV is to relieve excess pressure from a system or equipment to prevent overpressure situations. When the pressure exceeds the setpoint, the valve opens to discharge the excess pressure, protecting the system from damage.<\/p><p>\u2022 The valve operates automatically based on preset pressure levels. It opens when the pressure exceeds the setpoint and closes once the pressure returns to acceptable levels. This ensures continuous protection without the need for manual intervention.<\/p><p>\u2022 Many FMSRV models allow for the adjustment of the setpoint to suit specific pressure requirements. This provides flexibility in application and allows for customization based on the needs of the system.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c9c9c83 animated-slow elementor-invisible elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"c9c9c83\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-settings=\"{&quot;_animation&quot;:&quot;fadeInUp&quot;}\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<h3 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Benefits<\/h3>\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-9c36dfb elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget-mobile__width-inherit elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"9c36dfb\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"col-md-8\"><p>\u2022 The primary function of the FMSRV is to protect equipment, pipelines, and systems from overpressure situations by relieving excess pressure. This helps prevent catastrophic failures and ensures the safety of personnel and assets.<\/p><p>\u2022 The valve operates automatically in response to predetermined pressure levels. When the pressure inside the system exceeds the setpoint, the valve opens to discharge the excess pressure, thereby preventing damage to the system.<\/p><p>\u2022 FMSRVs are designed to relieve pressure rapidly and efficiently, minimizing the risk of equipment damage and ensuring the integrity of the system.<\/p><\/div>\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-e1b9a00 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"e1b9a00\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-se